## Design Approach

### Visual Style
- **Clean and professional** (not overly futuristic)
- **Data-focused** - Charts, graphs, statistics
- **Trust-building** - Real numbers, transparent metrics
- **Modern but accessible** - Professional gradient accents, readable fonts

### Color Palette
- Primary: Emerald green (success, money)
- Secondary: Dark blue/navy (trust, professionalism)
- Accent: Gold (premium, winning)
- Background: Dark with subtle depth

### Typography
- Headlines: Bold, clear, benefit-focused
- Body: Easy to read, professional
- Stats: Large, prominent, eye-catching

